an Amiga F1GP junkie's dream, set your web browser to:

   http://www.nanunanu.org/~oliver/AmigaF1.html

I can also be found lurking around on Internet Relay Chat (IRC) on the
#Amiga channel with nickname @{b}F1Oli@{ub}.
